課程概述 Course Description
       系統工程分析為一門探討系統建模(System modeling) 與系統響應(System response)的課程。系統」泛指擬探討的物 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    本課程的目的一方面在學習系統工程模型建立的相關知識，另一方面則探討該模型之特性，建立數學模型與物理系統間的關聯性，進而達到分析與設計該系統的目的。具體而言，本課程擬達成的目標如下：
(1)讓學生瞭解系統建模與系統響應之整體程序、數學模型建構與分析方法。
(2)讓學生瞭解電機、機械、造船、熱傳與流體等系統元件組成、動態特性與數學模型建立方法。
(3)讓學生瞭解單一系統與混合式系統之數學模型建立方法。
(4)藉由實際範例讓學生瞭解系統建模與系統響應之整體應用。    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Unit 1 Overview of system engineering -Formulation2Unit 1 Overview of system engineering -Solution technique3Unit 1 Overview of system engineering -Inputs4Unit 1 Overview of system engineering - System similarity5Unit 2 Modeling of system engineering - Mechanical systems6Unit 2 Modeling of system engineering - Electriacl systems7Unit 2 Modeling of system engineering - Fluid systems8Unit 2 Modeling of system engineering - Thermal systems9Unit 2 Modeling of system engineering - Mixed disciplines systems10Part 3 Dynamic response analysis - Frequency response11Part 3 Dynamic response analysis - Time response12Part 4 Controller Design - System stability analysis13Part 4 Controller Design - Steady-state disturbance sensitivity14Part 4 Controller Design - System compensation15Part 5 Engineering application - DC motor speed servo control16Part 5 Engineering application - Pneumatic position servo system17期中考18期末考 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


